a.n: Une Soirée de Poche: Run The Jewels

p.k: The Pocket Party series (Les Soirées de Poche) consists of musical sessions and concerts recorded in intimate settings. Discover a memorable performance by hip-hop duo Run the Jewels, recorded in Paris in 2014.
p.d: The Pocket Party series (Les Soirées de Poche) consists of musical sessions and concerts recorded in intimate settings. The many artists and bands that perform there are representatives of a wide range of musical styles, from jazz to soul, and funk to R&B. Discover a memorable performance by hip-hop duo Run the Jewels, recorded in Paris in 2014.
